title: Club dissapeared
body:

replies.body:
We'll need some tools in order to attempt to resolve this together. I recommend submitting a [**support ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) with this information so one of our specialists can work with you.

If you have any questions, let me know.
